<p>
Setting a custom schema is supported under the <code>show_in_rest</code> argument.<br />
</p>
<div class="wiki-code"><div class="code"><pre><span class="x">register_setting('name', 'group', [
    'show_in_rest' =&gt; [
        'schema' =&gt; [
            'type'       =&gt; 'object',
            'properties' =&gt; [
                'propA' =&gt; [
                    'type' =&gt; 'string',
                ]
            ]
        ]
    ]
]);
</span></pre></div></div>
